Class PowerGodDecorator

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.PSP43.server.controller.cards.AbstractGodCard
it.polimi.ingsw.PSP43.server.controller.cards.decorators.PowerGodDecorator
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
BlockRiseDecorator, BuildUnderFeetDecorator, SwapIfPossibleDecorator, SwapMoveDecorator, UnconditionedDomeBuildDecorator, WinFiveDomeDecorator, WinTwoFloorsFallDecorator
public abstract class PowerGodDecorator
extends AbstractGodCard
This decoration is made to add dinamically features to the cards, in order to give powers to the players' Gods and to limit their possibilities because of the opponents' Gods
